enhance the impact of your drill, or increase movement speed – choose carefully and strategize to increase odds of survival.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637320/extras/7d0f9bf132abd72b4e2de9c55faa6aaa.poster.avif?t=1771671327\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637320/extras/7d0f9bf132abd72b4e2de9c55faa6aaa.webm?t=1771671327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637320/extras/966d9776534b95c6899af48702a9d783.avif?t=1771671327\" width=780 height=140 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise your setup and find a playstyle that works for you by choosing from two unique keeper types, four different domes, and four primary gadgets. Pick a run modifier, adjust difficulty settings and discover dozens of secondary gadgets while you dig through the earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1637320/extras/c141de5c54fef9191dcff440b503f688.avif?t=1771671327\" width=780 height=1486 /></span></p>",
